==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Proprietor
<hw>Pro*pri"e*tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[For older
<ets>proprietary</ets>: cf. F. <ets>propri⟦eacute⟧tarie</ets>.]</ety>
<def>One who has the legal right or exclusive title to anything, whether
in possession or not; an owner; <as>as, the proprietor of farm or of a
mill</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proprietorial</ent>⟦br⟧
